			<title>Episode 171: Fun with 3MA</title>
            <link><![CDATA[http://threemovesahead.libsyn.com/episode-171-fun-with-3ma]]></link>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://quartertothree.com">Tom Chick</a>, SMG studios designer <a href="https://twitter.com/#!/davidvheron" target="_blank">David Heron</a>, and <a href="http://jonshaferondesign.com/" target="_blank">Jon Shafer</a> join Rob to reflect on their various issues with "fun" and how we relate to games. It's a rambling discussion about what we want from games, how we want to talk about them, and whether enjoyment is possible without fun.</p>]]></description>
